carefuel.util

Class FixedPathAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • carefuel.util.FixedPathAlgorithm

  • public class FixedPathAlgorithm
extends Object
    The algorithms is the fixed path algorithm taken from "To Fill or not to Fill: The Gas Station Problem" by Khuller et. al.(available at https://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?doid=1978782.1978791)

    • Method Detail

      • run

        public List<Node> run()
        2-parted algorithm. First part: find break points, which are the cheapest gas stations that can be reached with one tank fill. Second part: Find best tanking behavior on the fixed path.
        Returns:
        list of nodes with their assigned amount of gas to fill at a gas station.
